Male (based on 
allotype
and 
three paratypes
). Body length from 
466 to 492 µm
. Habitus, colour, rostrum, shape and ornamentation of cephalothorax, all pedigerous somites, ornamentation of last threeurosomites (
Fig. 26A, B
), caudal rami (
Fig. 26A, B
), antenna (
Fig. 29A
), labrum (
Fig. 27F
), paragnaths, mandibula (
Fig. 27F
), maxillula (
Fig. 27F
